title: DAZ3D - Kara Dress for Genesis 3
description:
The Kara Dress for Genesis 3 Female is a dress modeled to be slinky and curve hugging, perfect for just about any occasion, day or night. 

The Kara Dress has been smoothed and perfected for many of the G3 Female character shapes, but will auto-fit to any Genesis 3 Female morph using auto-follow in DAZ Studio 4.6 or higher. 

- Kara Dress (.duf)
- 14 Texture Presets (.duf)
- 12 Texture Maps (3000 x 3000)
- 7 Bump Map (3000 x 3000)

The dress contains several adjust/movement morphs, including:

Adj Back For Sitting
Adj Back Left
Adj Back Right
Adj Chest Left
Adj Chest Right
Adj Front Left
Adj Front Right
Adj Left
Adj Right

The material presets include shaders optimized for both 3Delight AND the Iray Render Engine
